  "text": "U. Wagner and I find open publication of this criticism of [CITATION_1] MW'] important to stimulate appearance of a complete proof. I also find this important to stimulate private discussions (among mathematicians working in the same area) before making claims in arxiv or journal submissions. This note might also be interesting as an example of an open discussion of a potentially controversial question, carried in full mutual respect of participants of the discussion.",
